---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Terms of Service | Core & Balance Pilates" description="Booking, cancellation, and studio terms for Core & Balance Pilates." noindex={true}>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-20 prose">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
    <div class="text-ink-muted leading-relaxed space-y-4">
      <p>Last updated July 2026. By booking a class with Core & Balance Pilates, you agree to the following terms.</p>
      <p><strong>Bookings & payment:</strong> All classes are paid online at time of booking via Stripe. Prices are shown
      in USD and include your reserved spot for the specific session and instructor listed.</p>
      <p><strong>Cancellations:</strong> You may cancel or reschedule up to 12 hours before class start for a full
      refund. Cancellations inside 12 hours are non-refundable.</p>
      <p><strong>Health & safety:</strong> Pilates involves physical exertion. By booking, you confirm you are physically
      able to participate and will inform your instructor of any injuries, pregnancy, or medical conditions before class.</p>
      <p><strong>Studio conduct:</strong> We reserve the right to refuse service to anyone who compromises the safety or
      experience of other members or staff.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
